node.title: Australia takes on USA in second friendly in Newcastle
node.alt: USA celebrate after scoring a goal against the Matildas
node.description: Fresh off a 3-0 victory over the Matildas on Saturday, the USA will be hoping to make it two from two when they take on the hosts in tonight's final friendly. Follow our live blog.
